<p><span style="color: #333"><strong>故事：</strong><em>It’s all coming back, you understand? I don't like it!</em></span></p>
<p><span style="color: #333"><strong>作者：</strong> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mrpines" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2241229); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2241229&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1600785008" alt="MrPines" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2241229)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mrpines" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2241229); return false;">MrPines</a></span></span></p>
<p><span style="color: #333"><strong>鸣谢：</strong> <span class="error-inline"><em>Dr Aers</em> does not match any existing user name</span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rounderhouse" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4187885); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4187885&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1600785008" alt="Rounderhouse" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4187885)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rounderhouse" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4187885); return false;">Rounderhouse</a></span></span></p>
<blockquote>
<ul>
<li><strong><span style="color: #090">这个故事只能有一个幸存者；你如何定义它取决于你自己。</span></strong></li>
<li><strong><span style="color: #090">这篇文章必须从万圣节前夜开始，在万圣节的日出期间结束。</span></strong></li>
</ul>
</blockquote>
<p><span style="color: #333">The forghetti spaghetti has <em>had</em> it with Halloween.</span></p>
<p><a href="/mrpines-author-page">More from this author</a></p>
</div>
<hr />
<div class="credit-back" style="text-align: center;">
<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/credit:backmodule/code/2" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="height:2em;width: 100%;margin: 0;padding: 0;border: 0;background: transparent;"></iframe></p>
